It was pretty sad, actually.

531
00:29:49,100 --> 00:29:54,200
而演讲人的讲话主题是垃圾
And the guy speaking is talking about garbage.

532
00:29:54,210 --> 00:29:55,920
-垃圾  -废物回收
- Garbage? - Recycling.

533
00:29:56,450 --> 00:30:00,270
